# Binary assets — Git must not normalize line endings on Windows or
# attempt to diff. Code-reviewer flagged this in Phase 8 (Task 4 review)
# after every WOFF2/WebP/PNG commit triggered the "LF will be replaced
# by CRLF the next time Git touches it" warning on Windows.
*.woff2 binary
*.woff  binary
*.ttf   binary
*.otf   binary
*.webp  binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.avif  binary
*.ico   binary
